snippet.title: Small Town Dreamer | Amber Marshall and Shaun Johnston | Heartland 812 | CBC
snippet.description:
Here is a throwback to Season 8 with Amber Marshall and Shaun Johnston talking about the story behind the song, "Small Town Dreamer" (Lyndy's Song)

About Heartland: Heartland is a family drama on CBC TV about a family dealing with the highs and lows of life on a horse ranch in the stunning the foothills of Alberta.
